Revision history for Lamashtu

0.01    Date/time
        First version, released on an unsuspecting world.
        - A optional Neti gate on the control socket, the enable_auth unix
          ownership challenge, with authed_users/authed_groups deciding who
          may drive the daemon. Off by default, where socket_group/socket_mode
          gate the socket as before. UID 0 always passes.

